{"tid":2323873,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇黃店賣聖誕卡（想入俾收押手足）","createTime":"2020-12-13T13:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T13:41:33.000Z","uid":45295,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"512cd2bfd6a1a67139479e82312174290d190241","tid":2323873,"uid":45295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"因為聖誕節就嚟 我有位朋友收押緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實除咗出面嘅人可以寫聖誕卡寄入去<br />\n探訪親友可以入日用品嗰時入10張聖誕卡連信封 俾佢寄返出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">但有好多限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 不可有任何附貼物，如絲帶、喱士、閃粉、貼紙等<br />\n2. 不可有額外裝置，如音樂裝罝、彈弓裝置、閃燈裝置等<br />\n3. 不可是立體設計、迷你咭，摺紙、有夾層（即兩層紙黐埋一層）<br />\n4. 尺寸不可大於 A4</span><br />\n<br />\n即係其實要普普通通嘅聖誕卡<br />\n但我個收押朋友又話唔想要太醜樣/卡通嗰啲<br />\n同時我又唔想去三中商/藍店買<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>請問有冇黃店/ig shop有賣聖誕卡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f233f3e54669d1da65c4033cd5ebe5e2c1a027ba","tid":2323873,"uid":45295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2febfa4a8b42b901257dea4f9ff3ef31202777","tid":2323873,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"深水埗有黃文具店呀"},{"pid":"8a3d5754931e2f46bf7cebca5e4a870c45dbc8d5","tid":2323873,"uid":138836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:36:51.000Z","msg":"你要幾多張呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f530830462d26e97e8d5b031210632ac3de352","tid":2323873,"uid":45295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a3d5754931e2f46bf7cebca5e4a870c45dbc8d5","tid":2323873,"uid":138836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:36:51.000Z","msg":"你要幾多張呀<img src=\"